dct_description_sm: From British surveys between 1878 and 1881 (with additions from Fiji Govt. surveys to 1915).
Depths shown by soundings; relief by hachures and spot heights.
Shows shoals, reefs, drainage, small islands.
Textual descriptions and navigational notes, such as "heavy breakers" and "wooded."
